te\u202fC** offers the best overall mix: solid decision\u2011making, proven calmness under pressure, and clear crew\u2011cooperation strengths, while his interpersonal drawbacks are less severe than the outright uncooperativeness shown by Candidate\u202fB or the moodiness and isolation of Candidate\u202fD. Candidate\u202fA, though technically strong, lacks evidence of reliability and calmness, which are non\u2011negotiable for this role.\n**My vote:** Candidate C\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
